[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0294","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0294.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0144","title":"Dan Bernstein QMail 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"QMail 1.0 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 SMTP 协议的 RCPT 命令指定大量收件人地址，导致 QMail 在处理过程中消耗过多系统资源（CPU 与内存），最终造成邮件服务瘫痪。该漏洞影响 Dan Bernstein QMail 1.0 及早期版本，CVSS 评分为 2.1，危害等级低。官方建议升级至 QMail 1.03 或更高版本进行修复。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0144"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.470","remediation":"升级到 netqmail 1.06 或应用 qmail-1.03 的 RCPT DoS 补丁；在 qmail-smtpd 中设置软限制参数 `MAXRCPTS`（如设为 100），限制单次 SMTP 会话的收件人数量；同时启用 `rcpthosts` 和 `morercpthosts` 控制邮件转发，防止被滥用为拒绝服务攻击的反射点。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://cr.yp.to/qmail/venema.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319024&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319029&w=2","http://www.ornl.gov/its/archives/mailing-lists/qmail/1997/06/threads.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2237","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/208","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20562","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0144.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0144","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0144.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0144.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0144.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-78g5-jc8q-wgq5/GHSA-78g5-jc8q-wgq5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2237/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0144.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0294.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0099","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0099.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0035","title":"多厂商 Unix ftpd 信号处理竞态条件漏洞","description":"ftpd 守护进程的信号处理例程中存在条件竞争漏洞（Race Condition），攻击者可利用信号处理时序差绕过文件访问控制，实现任意文件读取或写入。该漏洞影响多个 UNIX 系统中的 ftpd 实现，攻击者需与目标建立 FTP 连接并在特定操作窗口内触发竞态条件以完成利用，CVSS 评分 5.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0035"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.893","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.5.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了信号处理例程中的条件竞争问题。如无法升级，建议禁用 FTP 服务（systemctl disable vsftpd/wu-ftpd）或替换为 vsftpd/ProFTPD 等更安全的 FTP 守护进程。在不必要的情况下，可通过防火墙限制对 21 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0035"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0090","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0090.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0034","title":"Perl suidperl 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"suidperl（sperl）是 Perl 中用于执行 SUID 权限脚本的辅助程序，其在处理用户输入时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向目标系统提交特制的 Perl 脚本参数触发该溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Perl 4.x 及 5.x 版本，涉及 BSD/OS、RedHat、SGI 等多个操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0034"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.680","remediation":"升级 Perl 至 5.004 或更高版本以修复 suidperl 缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可移除 suidperl 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/suidperl），并改用 sudo 机制替代 setuid 脚本执行。长期建议彻底废弃 suidperl，使用常规 Perl 解释器配合 sudo 调用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0034","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19547","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0034","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0034.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6v5q-h64v-p5mp/GHSA-6v5q-h64v-p5mp.json","https://github.com/briandfoy/cpan-security-advisory/blob/b45d5ed44c1ca4a46a9138ebed1f2bec6deb0956/TO_DO","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0090.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0090.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0090.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0163","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0163.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0064","title":"IBM AIX lquerylv 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统的 lquerylv 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地低权限用户可通过向该程序发送精心构造的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 AIX 多个版本，需要本地用户身份才能利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0064"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.583","remediation":"立即安装 IBM AIX APAR IX73924 安全补丁，或升级至 AIX 4.2.1 及以上版本。若无法立即打补丁，可执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/lquerylv` 移除该程序的 setuid 位，以阻止本地普通用户通过此漏洞获取 root 权限；同时限制不可信用户的本地访问权限作为深度防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167418428&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/335","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0064.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0064","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0064.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0064.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0064.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mqqq-75g7-35v7/GHSA-mqqq-75g7-35v7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0163.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0096","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0096.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0036","title":"SGI IRIX login 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 及之前版本中的 /bin/login 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。当 LOCKOUT 参数设置为非零值时，攻击者可通过精心构造的输入触发缓冲区溢出，以 root 权限创建或破坏系统文件，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，利用门槛较低，危害严重。SGI 已发布安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0036"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.110","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 1997 年 5 月安全公告 19970508-02-PX 提供的修补补丁。临时缓解措施：在 /etc/default/login 配置文件中将 LOCKOUT 参数设为 0 并重启 login 服务。由于 SGI IRIX 已停止技术支持多年，建议尽快迁移至仍受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/h-106.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/990","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/557","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19310","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0036","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/dcc6735c9c3e50e93de820fa1ac9c54ecf6b2577/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-00xx/CVE-1999-0036.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0096.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0444","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0444.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0259","title":"cfingerd 用户信息泄露漏洞","description":"cfingerd 是一款可配置的 finger 服务守护程序，由于其未对用户查询进行充分的访问控制过滤，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 `search.**@target` 查询请求，枚举系统上所有已注册用户账号信息，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响使用 cfingerd 的 Unix/Linux 系统，攻击者可在未授权条件下远程利用，为进一步的社会工程学攻击或密码爆破提供用户列表基础。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0259"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.240","remediation":"升级 cfingerd 至 1.4.3 或更高版本以修复用户列表泄露漏洞；如无法升级，建议在 inetd/xinetd 配置中禁用 finger 服务（注释掉 finger 行），或使用 tcpwrappers（hosts.allow/hosts.deny）限制可访问源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0259","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0259.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0259.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0259","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0259.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0259.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/322.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/finger.rules","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m4g2-9rpr-wc96/GHSA-m4g2-9rpr-wc96.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/cfinger_search.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0444.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0101","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0101.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0037","title":"FreeBSD Metamail 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统自带的 metamail 邮件处理工具存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的 MIME 邮件消息，在消息头中嵌入恶意命令。当用户使用 metamail 处理该恶意邮件时，漏洞被触发，导致以当前用户权限在系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，但需要用户主动触发邮件处理操作，影响范围较广。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0037"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.340","remediation":"升级 metamail 至已过滤 MIME 邮件头 shell 元字符的修补版本；若无法升级，建议直接卸载 metamail（pkg delete metamail）并改用 procmail 或 maildrop 等现代邮件处理工具替代；同时配置邮件客户端不自动调用 metamail 处理来自不可信来源的 MIME 邮件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0037"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0101.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0100","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0039","title":"SGI IRIX webdist.cgi 命令执行漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 的 webdist.cgi 程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 distloc 参数中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符），即可绕过输入过滤执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.3 版本，攻击无需身份认证，仅需向目标 Web 服务发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，可导致服务器被完全控制。CVSS 评分 7.3，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0039"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.717","remediation":"建议从 SGI 安全公告 19970501-02-PX 获取并安装对应 IRIX 版本的补丁。如无法立即打补丁，应删除或禁用 CGI 目录下的 webdist.cgi 程序，并确保 webdist 服务已停止。对于仍在使用 SGI IRIX 的系统，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统，因为 IRIX 已于 2006 年 12 月停止技术支持，不再提供安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1997-12.html","http://www.osvdb.org/235","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/374","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/333","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19299","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0039","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0039.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/webdist.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-j78w-x657-xvr7/GHSA-j78w-x657-xvr7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.1175"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0100.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0100.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0253","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0253.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0112","title":"IBM AIX CDE dtterm 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 4.2 系统中的 CDE 桌面环境 dtterm 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。未授权本地攻击者可通过向 dtterm 程序传递特制的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖函数返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞要求攻击者拥有系统本地账号，影响 AIX 4.2 版本及可能更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0112"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.680","remediation":"建议升级至 AIX 4.3 及以上版本，或安装 IBM 提供的相应 APAR 补丁。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/dt/bin/dtterm 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/dtterm），并限制可执行该程序的用户组，仅授权可信用户访问 CDE 环境。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/878","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/333","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0112","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0112.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3xqj-xx96-hm93/GHSA-3xqj-xx96-hm93.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83084/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0112.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0253.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0102","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0102.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0040","title":"多厂商 X Window System libXt 库本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"X Window System 的 Xt 库中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用 libXt 库中 XtAppInitialize() 函数的溢出缺陷，通过精心构造的输入触发内存破坏，从而获取 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS、FreeBSD、HP-UX、AIX、IRIX、SunOS、UnixWare 等多种 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。由于利用条件仅需本地访问，在多用户环境下威胁较大，已有公开的 xterm 利用代码。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0040"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级各厂商已修复的 X11 发行版：FreeBSD 升级至 2.2.5 及以上版本或 3.x，HP-UX 安装 HP 对应安全补丁，AIX 安装 IBM APAR 对应补丁，IRIX 升级至 6.5 及以上版本并安装 SGI 安全补丁，Solaris 安装 Sun 对应补丁簇。如无法升级，移除所有 setuid root 的 X11 程序（如 /usr/bin/X11/xterm）的 suid 权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T08:41:11.703754812+00:00","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0102.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0103","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0103.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0038","title":"BSD xlock 缓冲区溢出本地代码执行漏洞","description":"BSD 操作系统中 xlock 屏幕锁定程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xlock 程序发送特制的超长输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的执行流程，实现以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多个 BSD 衍生系统，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，无需认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0038"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.473","remediation":"升级 xlock 至 xlockmore 2.5 及以上版本，或从操作系统厂商获取对应补丁（Sun 补丁 ID 10145）。在无法升级的环境中，限制不可信用户本地登录权限，移除 xlock 的 setuid root 权限位以阻止提权，或使用其他屏幕锁定工具替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0038"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0103.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0304","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0304.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0149","title":"SGI IRIX cgi-bin wrap 目录遍历漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 系统中的 cgi-bin wrap 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 URL 参数中使用 `..`（点点）序列绕过路径限制，访问并列出服务器上任意目录的内容。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，可导致敏感文件信息泄露，例如系统配置文件、用户数据等。攻击条件简单，仅需目标系统运行存在漏洞的 wrap CGI 程序即可实施。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0149"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-04-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.233","remediation":"建议升级至 SGI IRIX 6.3 及以上版本，或直接移除系统 cgi-bin 目录下的 wrap CGI 脚本。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器（如 Netscape FastTrack）配置中严格限制 cgi-bin 目录访问权限，并禁用路径穿越（..）与目录列表功能以作临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/247","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/373","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/290","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19298","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0149.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0149","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0149.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0149.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0149.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/UnAnnotated/CVE-1999-0149.xml","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/wrap.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0304.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0149","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0149.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0058","title":"PHP CGI 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"PHP 的 CGI 程序 php.cgi 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该溢出，导致内存损坏，从而获得目标服务器的 shell 访问权限。该漏洞影响早期版本的 PHP，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议用户升级至最新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0058"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.707","remediation":"立即升级至修复了 CGI 缓冲区溢出问题的 PHP 3.0.1 或更高版本；若无法升级，在 Apache 配置中通过 `<FilesMatch \"php\\.cgi\"> Deny from all </FilesMatch>` 禁用 php.cgi 的外部直接访问，并改用 mod_php 模块方式运行 PHP 脚本以消除 CGI 攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/712"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0149.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0105","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0105.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0042","title":"华盛顿大学 IMAP 与 POP 服务器缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"华盛顿大学实现的 IMAP 和 POP 服务器中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向运行 imapd 服务的 Linux 系统发送特制请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而造成远程代码执行或任意文件读取。该漏洞影响使用华盛顿大学实现 IMAP/POP 协议套件的 Linux 系统，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0042"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.303","remediation":"升级 UW IMAP 至 4.5 及以上版本，该版本修复了 imapd 及 popd 中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，建议禁用 IMAP/POP 服务，改用 SSH 隧道加密访问邮件，或在防火墙层面限制对 143/110 端口的访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0042","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/340","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0042","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0042.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/imap.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/imap_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83099/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-00xx/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0105.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0527","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0527.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0315","title":"Sun Solaris fdformat 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 fdformat 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。fdformat 是格式化软盘的工具，设置了 setuid root 权限。本地用户可通过向该命令传递超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.4 及更早版本，攻击者需要拥有本地 shell 访问权限，成功利用后可获得完全 root 控制权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0315"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.140","remediation":"建议升级到 Solaris 2.6 及以上版本，或安装 Sun 官方补丁 105401-01。临时缓解措施可移除 fdformat 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /bin/fdformat。限制本地用户对 fdformat 的访问权限亦可降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/138","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/328"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0527.toml"}]